She had been online for quite a while.  Since she was in a self 
sustained CR chamber, her awakening went unnoticed.  She was fully 
charged and was flying low to the ground in robot mode, searching 
for anyone she knew.  She then picked up two signatures, one she 
knew very well.  

"Windlord!" she called through her comm, flying toward his signal as 
fast as she could.
